{"tid":1222721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"終於明白要打贏輿論戰，就係要以其人之道 還治其人之身","createTime":"2019-06-14T13:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T19:41:56.000Z","uid":161430,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1d69efdbad91cacdf18f48029d299f9df41280","tid":1222721,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:48:26.000Z","msg":"第一，<span style=\"color: orange;\">一樣野講一百次就會變真</span><br />\n三毛最鍾意，屈你玩革命，文匯報屈有幾多人撐修訂撐警，<br />\n全部都係痴撚線咁搿硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n就咁岩，咁我地玩返勁fight，製造大量長輩圖啦，<br />\n呢條戰線就同你玩泥漿摔角，唔講仁義道德。<br />\n<br />\n第二，<span style=\"color: orange;\">對住咩人就講咩</span><br />\n保皇黨都識對住班中間派，廢中廢老講民生，<br />\n點解我地就唔識？<br />\n咁今次就以牙還牙用返民生同佢鬥講，<br />\n講逃犯條例一過，香港一定好有機會股市樓市暴跌，<br />\n外資一走，你一定份工都不保。<br />\n<br />\n泛民都應該要有所覺悟，<br />\n你永遠只係叫追求公義同可恥，<br />\n但好多蠢人根本唔知有咩咁可恥，<br />\n你講民主，咁你就解釋民主點影響班廢中廢老份工會不保、<br />\n血汗錢會冇曬，你要講呢d先係架！<br />\n<br />\n你想拉攏果個人，咁就講返果個人會關心既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838fcd8b5bf97ca1d45e2f8e23994f711404b934","tid":1222721,"uid":175540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:51:47.000Z","msg":"建制選舉個陣就話選建制會製造動亂影響經濟<br />\n整多幾張長輩圖叫佢地唔好投建制<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89de2610de4fb32f8e7c7093e761784d48e729c3","tid":1222721,"uid":261524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fe63b546873db85936cc66689362f401c2f823","tid":1222721,"uid":41245,